{"tid":713461,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"到底拗柴睇中定西好","createTime":"2018-06-22T21:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T05:45:22.000Z","uid":119839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e81e408652410258c3641411ca2b422b8d8a3d2d","tid":713461,"uid":119839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:30:34.000Z","msg":"四個月前拗到以家都未好哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多角度隻腳板去唔到硬哂 唔小心整到就痛 無另一隻腳咁受到力<br />\n又成日卡卡聲 腳踝有舊突起左既肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月睇過兩次中醫針炙個d 但係幾日之後都係無用<br />\n應該點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇專科會唔會好過中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1187b672cfab79826e7e2a76a9ea073c33a311b6","tid":713461,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:32:12.000Z","msg":"點忍到4個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614b978ec8fe7a147973d5cecbc905769cfa0c61","tid":713461,"uid":176763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:38:01.000Z","msg":"我兩個月前都拗柴 而家都係卡卡聲 踢波仲痛 唔知會唔會自然好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a978d4b55130415770fd0c5e2a57eef9b4c924","tid":713461,"uid":22952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T22:25:57.000Z","msg":"Why not both?<br />\n睇中醫護理好隻腳先 等佢復原<br />\n好返七成八成做返物理治療"},{"pid":"16cc1f0649183b7c98310ba572f1dbfe079fac14","tid":713461,"uid":73660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:12:15.000Z","msg":"推推推推，同樓上一樣4個幾月前咬到，咩角度都扭到，但就內側條筋仲係隱隱作痛咁，連落腳跟有d痹，行路行耐d條筋就會酸痛，咩醫生都睇過哂，諗住過多個月再去骨科複診，連登有無神醫介紹"},{"pid":"65c7fecfbc14cfdd78b1518e624e11e26ba55f29","tid":713461,"uid":168534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:26:03.000Z","msg":"西喇唔好傻<br />\n當年斷acl 好後悔冇即刻睇骨醫<br />\n中醫根本斷唔到你傷邊到"},{"pid":"094ca32dde2dd787ef8f7a2b4ce068894f96c5c7","tid":713461,"uid":33487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"睇鐵打要識搵 我搵個師傅係軍醫黎<br />\n所以依家我都認同中醫多d<br />\n當年半月板c裂 去左照磁力共震 西醫話抖一個月就可以打番波 鐵打叫我抖半年+拎拐掌3個月 真係好彩聽鐵打講先無事"}]}